9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Dracula | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"In late 15th-century Eastern Europe, Prince Vlad II’s bride is brutally murdered. As a result, he renounces God and damns Heaven itself. Cursed with eternal life, Vlad is reborn as Dracula, an immortal warlord who defies fate in a blood-soaked crusade to wrench his lost love back from death."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148224/dracula"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Dracula"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"In late 15th-century Eastern Europe, Prince Vlad II’s bride is brutally murdered. As a result, he renounces God and damns Heaven itself. Cursed with eternal life, Vlad is reborn as Dracula, an immortal warlord who defies fate in a blood-soaked crusade to wrench his lost love back from death."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/148224/dracula"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/libhghrUSBSEdHgF9uP1SQES0nQ.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Dracula"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"In late 15th-century Eastern Europe, Prince Vlad II’s bride is brutally murdered. As a result, he renounces God and damns Heaven itself. Cursed with eternal life, Vlad is reborn as Dracula, an immortal warlord who defies fate in a blood-soaked crusade to wrench his lost love back from death."}],["$","meta","13",{"name":"twitter:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/libhghrUSBSEdHgF9uP1SQES0nQ.